# auto-dev

## Context Profile

Load core workspace policy. Each stage then loads only its own detailed context profile; do not preload all lifecycle documents.

## Contract

1. Execute `plan`, obtain and verify the SPEC-ID, then execute `go`, then `sync`.
2. Forward `--auto`, `--loop`, `--team`, `--multi`, `--quality`, `--model`, and `--variant` consistently; explicit user flags override defaults.
3. Preserve every mandatory phase/gate and stop at the first blocker with a resumable next step.
4. Do not mark sync complete until the Outcome Lock, mandatory requirements, Must acceptance, and Completion Debt gates pass.
5. Report lifecycle state and evidence after each stage.
